{"tid":1313013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tempo:「我們堅決擁護“一國兩制」","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:05:15.000Z","uid":161656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47c4b51d5401121d72a004548c3b81cd3e6d94cd","tid":1313013,"uid":161656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"說明：謝謝社會各界對Tempo的關注。目前,Tempo上半年在中國香港地區的電視廣告投放已於2019年6月13日正常結束，並不是臨時決策。就此前&ldquo;重新檢視宣傳策略&rdquo;的表達，意為公司常規的投放後所推進的評估流程。若因此導致大家的誤讀，我們表示衷心的歉意。未來，我們將會根據市場行銷策略如常進行香港地區的電視廣告（含TVB）投放。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感謝社會各界對此事件的關心。我們堅決擁護&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;的方針</span></span>，與香港各界人士共同維護香港繁榮穩定和諧的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/143477305672694/posts/2446847308669004?s=750520003&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F143477305672694%2Fposts%2F2446847308669004%3Fs%3D750520003%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e84a5c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/143477305672694/posts/2446847308669004?s=750520003&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e25dbe926bc388ab9d38de8d55bb67e3de27f106","tid":1313013,"uid":161656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vnbKWK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vnbKWK.png&h=c9ae24e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來有台灣制造紙巾牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cedd7483f3d3f9ec2c782846febbe80f2e162e","tid":1313013,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"393fed69c4a81540f66fe942d4cb5a8f0e7d6637","tid":1313013,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"我估計某程度上係本身電視越嚟越少人睇導致依個決定"}]}